# .env - Development Environment Variables
# 
# This file is for local development ONLY.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# IMPORTANT: .env should NEVER be committed to Git.
#
# For GitHub Actions / CI:
# Set these as Repository Secrets instead (Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions)
#
# How to use:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.template .env
# 2. .env will be read automatically (gitignored)
# 3. For Dart: values are read via String.fromEnvironment() in ads_config.dart
# 4. For Android: values are read from build.gradle.kts

